HEADWORD: Triadelphous
<hw>Tri`a*del"phous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>tri-</ets> + Gr. <?/ brother.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Having
stamens joined by filaments into three bundles. See <xex>Illust.</xex>
under <er>Adelphous</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
